properties.hoMallDescription: Akasya’nın misafirleri dünya çapındaki markalarla keyifli bir alışveriş deneyimi yaşarken eğlenceli sosyal aktivitelerle ziyaretlerini zenginleştiriyor. 10 dönümlük parkı, metro, metrobüs ve Marmaray ile kolay ulaşımı Akasya’yı sadece Anadolu Yakası’nın değil tüm İstanbul’un en popüler buluşma noktalarından biri haline getiriyor. Şehrin ortasında ama kargaşadan uzak vakit geçirme imkânı sunan Akasya, her kategoriden seçkin markalarıyla misafirlerine ayrıcalıklı bir alışveriş deneyimi sunuyor.
properties.hoMallDescription_en: Turkey's and the world's best-known and most admired brings together the brands of guests Acacia New Generation Life Complex, pleasant shopping experience, rich social life options and metro with the 10-acre park, Metrobus, and both the Anatolian side of the Marmaray transport facilities, as well was opened as the most ambitious project of Istanbul. welcomes its guests with rich and leading brands in its sector such as ready-to-wear, health, beauty, cosmetics, shoes, bags, accessories, home decorations, cafe, restaurant, hypermarket. Fauchon, the famous cafe & delicatessen brand of France, which will enter the Turkish retail world for the first time, will meet its guests in Akasya with its first store in Istanbul, which will include all of America's most famous home decoration brand, Crate & Barrel, and the world-famous Victoria's Secret Pink Collection.
